name: Memento Mauri #7
description: This Soul brings strength to a whole new meaning. Countless years of Combat Training, even Childhood was filled with lessons on bringing an opponent to submission. At the Age of 13, this young Soul was more of a small Titan, hulking above the competition. In his Older Age, He wields a Two-Handed Bludgeon fashioned from a Pillar that supported his Childhood Home.
